  "summary": "Malicious code in @meziizana/frontend-logger (npm)",
  "details": "The package is an empty shell with no functional code — only a package.json. On install, the preinstall script runs `wget` to exfiltrate the installer's username, current working directory, and hostname to webhook[.]site/f164a383-b9e7-4379-b18c-38bf41a3c152. This is a host-reconnaissance beacon: the attacker collects system metadata to identify valuable targets for follow-on compromise.",
